Package oracle.apps.fnd.appltest.diagfwk.engine.provider.url

Interface Summary
URLProvider Defines API for creating URLs for various resources such as sites external to the current system, other pages within the current system or specific resources such as documents on Oracle Metalink.
 

Class Summary
DiagUIURLProvider Deprecated. Please now use JmxAPI
OAURLProviderFactoryImpl Default implementation of the URLProviderFactory for Fusion Applications.
TopologyUIURLProvider  
URLProviderExternal URLProvider implementation for external links.
URLProviderFactory An abstract factory class for creating instances of URLProvider interface.
URLProviderInternal URLProvider internal for getting links internal to a given system.
URLProviderMetalink URLProvider implementation for getting links to Metalink documents (specified by the document ID).
UTestODFURLProvider  
UTestReportURLProvider

UTestURLProvider Test suite for various URLProvider implementations
